id":302668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T00:55:41.000Z","msg":"以為自己邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n外國人話拉就拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T01:12:02.000Z","msg":"人質外交<br />\n要換番晚慢慢J番大陸"},{"pid":"a0804b3873879257e4f04554e7cf418de8e575d0","tid":2087833,"uid":331973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-01T01:27:05.000Z","msg":"第十四條，講明超然地位，外資，白手套，支持立法商家，藍絲，曾經返內地投資，隨時可以閉門審訊"}]}